  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386800/extras/d4bcb23da5a52fb6ad76364b120185da.poster.avif?t=1735410354\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386800/extras/d4bcb23da5a52fb6ad76364b120185da.webm?t=1735410354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386800/extras/d4bcb23da5a52fb6ad76364b120185da.mp4?t=1735410354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Silent Snowfall</strong> — a first-person horror game.<br><br> Christmas night turns into a nightmare when you find yourself in a mysterious house hiding chilling secrets. Its creaking hallways and dark rooms seem deserted, but every rustle and shadow hints at someone's presence.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386800/extras/1c4c7e3f75aeed10eb9ddc6cc20d9e55.poster.avif?t=1735410354\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386800/extras/1c4c7e3f75aeed10eb9ddc6cc20d9e55.webm?t=1735410354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386800/extras/1c4c7e3f75aeed10eb9ddc6cc20d9e55.mp4?t=1735410354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Can you survive uncovering the secrets of a house that is never truly empty? <br> <br>Game Features: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Realistic graphics </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Frightening atmosphere </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Tense sound design </p>",
